headline: Canada’s Industry Minister Meets With Saab, Ericsson in Sweden
summary: Joly is pushing for investment in Canadian industries amid damaging US tariffs, while emphasizing the government’s plan to increase defense spending.  The minister expects to speak with Saab about the Gripen E fighter jet, said the person, who asked not to be named in order to speak about private discussions.
